'''贾雅·巴克罕'''（[[印地語|印地語]]：जया बच्चन，[[英語|英語]]：Jaya Bachchan，婚前名為：Jaya Badhuri，{{bd|1948年|4月9日|catIdx=B}}）是一名[[印度|印度]]政治家及女演員。<ref>{{Cite web|title=I'm too upfront for politics: Jaya Bachchan|url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/bollywood/news-interviews/Im-too-upfront-for-politics-Jaya-Bachchan/articleshow/5531466.cms|access-date=2021-10-13|date=2010-02-03|publisher=The Times of India|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100602093730/http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/bollywood/news-interviews/Im-too-upfront-for-politics-Jaya-Bachchan/articleshow/5531466.cms|archive-date=2010-06-02}}</ref>巴克罕的丈夫是印度超級巨星[[阿米塔布·巴沙坎|阿米塔布·巴沙坎]]，兒子[[阿彼锡·巴克罕|阿彼锡·巴克罕]]及媳婦[[艾西瓦娅·巴克罕|艾西瓦娅·巴克罕]]均是[[寶萊塢|寶萊塢]]的知名演員<ref>{{Cite web|title=Amitabh Bachchan away from wife Jaya on 41st wedding anniversary|url=https://indianexpress.com/article/entertainment/bollywood/amitabh-bachchan-away-from-wife-jaya-on-41st-wedding-anniversary/|access-date=2021-10-13|date=2014-06-03|work=The Indian Express|language=en|archive-date=2021-10-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211029050737/https://indianexpress.com/article/entertainment/bollywood/amitabh-bachchan-away-from-wife-jaya-on-41st-wedding-anniversary/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=All is Well Between Aishwarya Rai and Jaya Bachchan, Saas-Bahu Jodi Talks in Bengali|url=https://www.ibtimes.co.in/all-well-between-aishwarya-rai-jaya-bachchan-saas-bahu-jodi-talks-bengali-606229|access-date=2021-10-13|date=2014-08-06|last=Sarkar|first=Prarthna|publisher=IBTimes India|language=en|archive-date=2021-10-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211030090338/https://www.ibtimes.co.in/all-well-between-aishwarya-rai-jaya-bachchan-saas-bahu-jodi-talks-bengali-606229|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在成為政治家之前，巴克罕是一名知名女演員並曾三次成為[[印度電影觀眾獎|印度電影觀眾獎]]的最佳女主角得獎者。她在1992年獲得印度政府頒發的[[莲花士勋章|莲花士勋章]]。

巴克罕在1971年出道，首部電影是電影《Guddi》。1973年結婚及生子後，她開始減少工作並間中接拍少量電影。

